Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.40,0:00:21.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事隔八年看見哥哥的面容
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.46,0:00:23.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是殺人者的嘴臉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.24,0:00:29.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕我也是同樣的嘴臉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.08,0:00:32.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前的Freyja真的是你發射的?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.66,0:00:36.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 原本打算阻止哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.39,0:00:40.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便殺死哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.97,0:00:46.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不能把Freyja 把這Damocles的鑰匙交給哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.28,0:00:48.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算被哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.95,0:00:50.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使用了GEASS
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.41,0:00:54.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對娜娜莉使用GEASS?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.24,0:00:59.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 我期望過無數次
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.12,0:01:02.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪怕只讓娜娜莉重見光明
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.94,0:01:09.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 王者的力量 絕對服從的GEASS也無法對娜娜莉使用
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.03,0:01:11.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那現在呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.23,0:01:12.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.15,0:01:16.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果再扭曲娜娜莉的意志 我就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.50,0:02:52.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,RE;
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.91,0:03:01.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡蓮 無論如何都要阻撓嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.75,0:03:04.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朱雀 我誤會了你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.39,0:03:11.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本以為作法不同 你也在以你的方式為日本著想
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.40,0:03:11.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.40,0:03:16.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和魯魯修有必須完成的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.66,0:03:19.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎 這麼想要力量嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.11,0:03:21.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.22,0:03:21.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.25,0:03:24.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不該留在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.37,0:03:26.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,擊敗你 阻止魯魯修
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.95,0:03:28.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會讓你如願
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.63,0:03:42.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,利瓦爾不去逃難嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.22,0:03:44.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要逃去哪?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.02,0:03:46.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這倒也是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.59,0:03:52.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能和大家每天過得開心就滿足了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.06,0:03:53.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.04,0:03:58.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有主君的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.99,0:04:00.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總是依靠著誰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.90,0:04:01.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脆弱的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.68,0:04:11.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別去 您這傷…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.23,0:04:14.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必須為起始的責任負責
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.43,0:04:16.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作為領導者的資格
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.90,0:04:20.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥沒有掌握這個世界的資格
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.76,0:04:24.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自稱ZERO踐踏人意志的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.78,0:04:29.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就該繼續逃亡生活嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.18,0:04:32.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要終日為逃避暗殺而奔波的未來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.69,0:04:34.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了你的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.37,0:04:37.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我什麼時候懇求過那種事?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.07,0:04:41.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只要和哥哥在一起生活就足夠
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.25,0:04:45.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 現實被各種因素所支配
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.51,0:04:47.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抗爭是必不可少的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.30,0:04:50.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為此 才作為反抗組織戰鬥至今
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.31,0:04:53.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理應也有組織中實現的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.73,0:04:59.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些無法加入組織和系統的人該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.81,0:05:03.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在怎麼能斷言這是錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.94,0:05:05.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.65,0:05:08.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別居高臨下教訓人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.56,0:05:12.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能進入組織的人該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.69,0:05:13.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所謂正義…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.87,0:05:19.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果服從侵略者的做法 就等於承認他們的行為
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.00,0:05:22.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是現在出擊會死
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.69,0:05:24.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就算這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.43,0:05:29.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.71,0:05:33.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只懂得這種活法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.32,0:05:37.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,藤堂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.74,0:05:40.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼要爭鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.83,0:05:43.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要還有必須保護之人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.97,0:06:01.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也許失去了對戰爭應有的矜持與美學
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.44,0:06:05.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便這樣也必須有容身處
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.78,0:06:08.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只為此戰鬥到現在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.65,0:06:11.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直人 我們這樣做對嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.47,0:06:17.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但人稱戰爭是發明之母
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.20,0:06:18.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不承認
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.53,0:06:22.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布丁伯爵沒有看到人在其中的作用
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.26,0:06:23.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是叫妮娜來著?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.88,0:06:25.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎麼說?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.11,0:06:28.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是盡自己所能
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.58,0:06:30.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不想重蹈覆轍而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.33,0:06:34.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但人是脆弱的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.20,0:06:37.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 有夢想錯了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.70,0:06:40.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道我連這資格都沒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.47,0:06:42.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明還能幹下去 能幹下去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.94,0:06:45.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼大家都看不起我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.52,0:06:46.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.84,0:06:51.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看見了 看到現在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.46,0:06:54.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抗爭就是人類的歷史
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.17,0:06:54.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.97,0:06:59.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人和世界是如此難以如人所願
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.02,0:07:01.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你就想人家都聽你的?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.88,0:07:02.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.48,0:07:04.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是卑劣的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.48,0:07:08.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扭曲人心 踐踏人尊嚴的GEASS
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.78,0:07:10.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那Damocles又如何
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.18,0:07:14.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,強制令人俯首稱臣的系統 就不卑劣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.59,0:07:18.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Damocles會成為仇恨的象徵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.54,0:07:22.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仇恨會彙集於此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.61,0:07:24.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了讓大家能迎接明天
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.64,0:07:29.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎 娜娜莉你也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.82,0:07:30.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.04,0:07:33.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魯魯修．V．布里塔尼亞下令
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.01,0:07:36.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把Damocles的鑰匙給我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.43,0:07:49.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.57,0:07:52.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能交給哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.25,0:07:56.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能再 罪上加罪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.74,0:08:03.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請吧 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.94,0:08:08.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,耍小聰明
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.79,0:08:10.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紀錄完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.70,0:08:14.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還早呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.51,0:08:18.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爆散
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.47,0:08:22.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紀錄下來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.92,0:08:24.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傑雷米亞．哥特瓦爾德
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.50,0:08:30.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帶給你敗北的 有紀念意義的男人之名
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.77,0:08:33.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紀念? 那和我無關
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.57,0:08:36.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正我沒有記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.41,0:08:37.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,記憶?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.12,0:08:39.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.87,0:08:43.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,動起來 Tristan
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.85,0:08:45.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪怕只能飛也好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.70,0:08:50.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這下輻射波動也用盡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.59,0:08:54.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,護盾能量也耗完了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.47,0:08:55.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.91,0:09:06.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贏不了?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.36,0:09:08.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連GEASS的詛咒都用上了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.57,0:09:10.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡蓮 如此強大
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.64,0:09:12.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明是這邊的規格比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.12,0:09:17.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朱雀 有這樣的力量 為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.87,0:09:23.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結束吧 卡蓮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.37,0:09:28.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你如果有正義的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.18,0:09:42.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會 沒打到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.22,0:09:45.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 你打到了 卡蓮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.49,0:10:03.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎 你贏了 卡蓮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.62,0:10:10.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,娜娜莉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.26,0:10:14.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你已經在靠自己的意志活著
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.85,0:10:18.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我也能走自己的路
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.01,0:10:26.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.51,0:10:29.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我愛你 娜娜莉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.66,0:10:38.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你用了吧 GEASS
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.13,0:10:43.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.70,0:10:51.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 站住
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.22,0:10:59.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥是惡魔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.75,0:11:02.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卑劣 無恥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.36,0:11:07.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這…太過分
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.42,0:11:13.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,背叛者樞木朱雀已敗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.07,0:11:15.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你無意求生嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.58,0:11:16.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了那位大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.94,0:11:21.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神樂耶 你最近才得知魯魯修的真面目
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.59,0:11:22.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這又如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.74,0:11:26.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但卻理解他的一部分本質
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.26,0:11:28.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真是溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.47,0:11:37.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通告全世界
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.41,0:11:41.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是神聖布里塔尼亞帝國皇帝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.19,0:11:43.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魯魯修．V．布里塔尼亞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.14,0:11:49.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能 魯魯修使用了Freyja代表…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.77,0:11:50.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.90,0:11:52.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,騙人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.34,0:11:55.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修奈澤爾已加入我麾下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.54,0:12:00.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至此 Damocles與Freyja也全部為我所用
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.24,0:12:04.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑騎士團不再擁有與我對抗的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.58,0:12:09.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣也要垂死掙扎的話 招待你們的只會是Freyja
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.47,0:12:14.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經無人能阻我霸業
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.01,0:12:20.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 今天這一瞬間 世界已陷落我手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.31,0:12:28.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魯魯修．V．布里塔尼亞下令
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.34,0:12:31.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界啊 臣服於我吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.47,0:12:33.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,All Hail Lelouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.52,0:12:35.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,All Hail Lelouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.74,0:12:37.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,All Hail Lelouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.75,0:12:39.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,All Hail Lelouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.18,0:12:54.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神聖布里塔尼亞帝國第99代唯一皇帝陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.60,0:13:00.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兼黑騎士團C.E.O. 超合眾國第2代最高評議會議長
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.05,0:13:03.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魯魯修．V．布里塔尼亞陛下出現在我們眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.79,0:13:06.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.61,0:13:11.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反對魯魯修陛下的愚昧之徒 正被送往刑場
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.42,0:13:16.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上次大戰中 帝都Pendragon和眾多將士
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.60,0:13:21.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,包括Knight of Zero樞木朱雀卿在內 付出了慘重的犧牲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.97,0:13:25.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,E.U.批准超合眾國憲章
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.45,0:13:30.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們的魯魯修陛下 終於實現了世界統一偉業
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.78,0:13:32.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光榮與魯魯修陛下同在
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.95,0:13:34.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,All Hail Britannia!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.78,0:13:36.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,All Hail Lelouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.85,0:13:38.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼光榮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.46,0:13:39.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,單純的獨裁吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.80,0:13:41.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反抗者全部被殺死
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.84,0:13:45.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噓 被人聽到的話會滿門抄斬
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.85,0:13:49.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然不得不把這種內容作為正義報導
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.58,0:13:53.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魯魯修 這就是你想做的事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.65,0:13:56.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,支配世界和人們
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.99,0:13:59.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們也真傻
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.30,0:14:01.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當時何必與魯魯修頂嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.95,0:14:04.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為迎來明天
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.61,0:14:08.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算重複著成功與失敗也必須前行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.48,0:14:11.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人和科學是一樣的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.48,0:14:13.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是進化
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.06,0:14:15.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是進步 布丁伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.52,0:14:17.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個稱呼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.94,0:14:19.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還在記恨嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.69,0:14:21.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你猜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.86,0:14:27.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羅伊德先生和拉克夏塔以前發生過什麼事?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.48,0:14:29.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是些瑣碎的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.80,0:14:32.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在想想根本不算什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.95,0:14:34.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出發點而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.48,0:14:45.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扇
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.62,0:14:49.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在出去正中他們下懷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.38,0:14:50.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.44,0:14:54.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.10,0:15:04.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.92,0:15:05.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.39,0:15:07.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.10,0:15:09.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,騙人 魯魯修在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.58,0:15:20.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道魯魯修他們策劃的是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.08,0:15:30.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別開槍 我來對付他
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.98,0:15:38.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧 假面騎士
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.68,0:15:43.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蠢貨
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.65,0:15:54.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朱雀 按約定你來殺死我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.00,0:15:56.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論如何都要做嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.54,0:16:01.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,按預定 世界的仇很正集中在我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.87,0:16:05.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要我消失 就能斬斷這仇恨的鎖鏈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.87,0:16:11.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑騎士團留有ZERO的傳說
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.83,0:16:13.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修奈澤爾也會聽命於ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.48,0:16:20.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣世界將不再用軍事力量 而是在談判桌上就能解決
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.59,0:16:22.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能朝明天前進
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.36,0:16:29.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.61,0:16:33.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,零之鎮魂曲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.95,0:16:38.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在C的世界中 我們明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.03,0:16:41.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人們期望著明天
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.81,0:16:44.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吶 朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.29,0:16:46.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不覺得願望和GEASS很像嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.36,0:16:54.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,靠自己無法實現的事會尋求他人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.58,0:16:56.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,願望嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.30,0:17:01.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就對所有人使用名為願望的GEASS
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.17,0:17:03.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了世界的明天
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.43,0:17:13.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魯魯修 你作為對人使用GEASS的代價
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.18,0:17:20.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有被殺的覺悟 才有資格開槍
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.76,0:17:30.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朱雀 你要成為英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.46,0:17:31.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從世界的敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.40,0:17:35.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皇帝魯魯修．V．布里塔尼亞手中拯救世界的救世主
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.67,0:17:37.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.14,0:17:50.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魯…魯魯修
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.77,0:17:53.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這對你來說也是懲罰
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.21,0:18:02.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你必須作為正義的使者戴著面具活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.44,0:18:07.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不再是樞木朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.35,0:18:15.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也必須為世界犧牲常人該有的幸福 永遠
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.32,0:18:19.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這份GEASS 我確實收到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.66,0:18:40.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.11,0:18:57.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會…哥哥之前都是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.37,0:19:02.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥 我愛你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.94,0:19:12.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…毀滅世界…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.00,0:19:21.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,創造…世界…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.01,0:19:27.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.15,0:19:31.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,睜開眼睛 哥哥 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.49,0:19:34.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔王魯魯修已死
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.75,0:19:36.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,釋放人質
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.00,0:19:43.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好 撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.30,0:19:44.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暫且撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.34,0:19:48.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道那是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.45,0:19:49.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.63,0:19:52.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是 ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.43,0:19:56.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,耍賴 我有哥哥就夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.14,0:20:02.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有哥哥的明天…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.29,0:20:52.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魯魯修
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.33,0:20:56.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那之後世界好了不少
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.86,0:21:02.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用在戰爭上的能源 現在用在饑餓與貧困
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.31,0:21:07.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各種仇恨與罪名都被被你一手包辦了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.76,0:21:16.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家比起Damocles這個系統 更容易記住一個有名有姓的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.62,0:21:19.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真夠可笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.35,0:21:27.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 正因為如此 大家才不會被過去束縛 能繼續前進
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.82,0:21:31.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你又會笑著說「如我所料」了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.88,0:21:36.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然還留下了各種問題
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.16,0:21:38.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.18,0:22:16.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,名為GEASS的王的力量 會令人孤獨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.29,0:22:20.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是好像不太對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.82,0:22:23.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧 魯魯修
